As for the soloing part, yea we are great at soloing. The only thing that druids have over us is that they can quad kite, and the only thing that necros have is that they can fear kite. But with our massive earth pet tank and our high damage DDs, we can take down some big mobs. The necros can do a lot of damage, but their spells are mainly DoTs and so their fights are long, just like the druids too. We go in, hit hard, hit fast, and the mobs die fast so we can gain xp quicker.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uwinterbreath.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Winterbreath</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#333333>(5/2/01 2:12:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=207.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.funhouse.ugate.net/everquest/wuoshi.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Can Mages Solo with the best of them ?</span><hr size=1> If you don't mind sitting on your Arse medding and waiting for 9/10 of your EQ life and leveling at a snails pace then soloing is for you.. yes we CAN solo but its slow and painful and very unfun.  If your Eq playstyle doesn't allow you to group a lot I recommend trying a bard. they are hands-down the best soloers in the game. <p><P><a href="mailto:winterbreath@shadowstrike.com">Winterbreath</a>, Chaos Mage of Xegony<br>
